title: Dairy-Free Hummingbird Cake
ingredients: ['375g plain flour', '400g caster sugar', '1 teaspoon bicarbonate of soda', '1/2 teaspoon salt', '1 teaspoon ground cinnamon', '300ml vegetable oil', '3 eggs', '225g tinned crushed pineapple with juice', '300g diced bananas', '115g chopped pecans', '1 teaspoon vanilla extract']
